\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Who used to read the story then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well - one person set apart - it all depends how many there was there you see, and - some would be the wheel
 of the coach, another'd be the hub, and - different parts of the coach, and - yes, and you'd got to stand up you see. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What were the forfeits you had to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Anything you'd got to pay a forfeit and then you had to do whatever they said, tel
l you to do. Somebody would read the forfeits out. That's when we'd have big parties you know and lots there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 When did you have big parties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well Christmastime and birthdays and - once now and again. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 At other times as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 YES. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were they friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Both. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have books about the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Story books. Yes. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember your parents reading much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, not a lot, no they're - not one for books you know. The papers of course, you know, daily papers but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, not much in the magazine. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What paper did your dad take, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Daily Express. Mm. I do remember that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did mother read the paper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did they ever read aloud to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No, not a lot. No, I wouldn't say they read - aloud not very much you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember reading to your brother at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you like doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you ever remember a funeral in the family before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well, yes, we - you - you mean when I'm young, when I was young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, when you were small.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I can't say that I do, not when I was - very young. No, I was older when my grandparents died, and of c
ourse I didn't know my mother's parents, they died before - before she married, about - well one of them - her mother did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 When did your grandparents die, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I can't tell you ex - not the exact year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 About how old were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 I can't remember. I was - I suppose I was - in me twenties, I'm not sure. Yes, think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 We've talked already about your brother, you can't remember him, you can remember him dying but not the funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Not the funeral, no, no, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You were sent away to your grandparents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, that's right. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were you ever taken out visiting neighbours and friends?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. I was taken out to - for relations, and Sunday evenings in the summertime it was a recognized thing to
 go out for walks - in the country lanes you know. All of us, the four of us, we used to go. But - oh - but there were times in the winter when we used to go to see our aunts you know and - their families.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How did you travel to see these people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Oh we had to walk. We walked most of - it isn't very often - not very often go on a bus, you know, and it's quite a way. But - I remember when I was very young we used to go in the pony and trap. When I was very young. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would that have been yours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
No. No. Oh it was borrowed. My - I had a great aunt that had a pony and trap and - she used to come and fetch me and take - and take me over to Batford, that's old Harpenden, where she lived there and - we used to go over there occasionally and sto
p for a week and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. I used to like being over there. Sometimes it was much longer. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You weren't homesick there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You went on your own did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, she took me you know, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Not with your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How old would you have been then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Six. Five and six, and even quite small, when I was four, you know, quite small I remember going over. 'Cos she wanted to adopt me. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 She hadn't any children of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes she had, but they'd all grown up. Yes, it was my mother's aunt you see. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And she wanted to adopt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Mm, she wanted to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 She was very fond of you was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 YES. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And you were of her too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. But my mother wouldn't do it of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 She was fond of you too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. She didn't want it, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember them talking about it when you - were little, about the possibility of you being adopted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No. I - oh no, I wasn't worried because I knew I wasn't going to be but she just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You felt quite safe at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you used to go shopping with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Oh yes, Saturdays. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you used to go to market?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, we used to go to the shops and
 market and mum and dad too. Mum and dad used to go shopping and - we all used to go. Used to take us with them - shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did mother do a weekly shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, mostly. Although - used to go to the shop nearly every day for something. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you ever remember going out just-with your father without mother, did he ever take you out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well, yes, I guess there has been - occasions you know. But -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did he take you on treats by yourself ever? Or did you all go together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Mostly went together. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you used to do special things on Bank Holidays, things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. We used to go out - for the day - usually excursions. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 By coach or train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, it would be by train - those - 'cos there wasn't so many co
aches not then, it was train mostly, and - on August Tuesday, 'cos August used to be - Bank Holiday week, August, the first week in August, and August Tuesday my father used to hire a - a pony and trap and we used to go to Hitchin. That was a regular Augu
st Tuesday treat, but we used to go for days, out for days, we didn't have a - we didn't go away for a holiday, unless it was to any relation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Where did you go on other excursions by train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, Yarmouth once. Mm. And Southend used to be quite a popular - one you know by train. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you like them, you looked forward to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And you all went, all four of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have those treats even later on when father was out of work,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Out of work, yes, yes. No he was in work -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 He had a regular job when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Yes. YES. He was really. It was before I came along I think he was out of work and - and then later on, it was in - 19 - well it'd be 1929 'cos he died in 1931. And it was be
tween 1928 and '31 'cos my mother moved - into Felix Avenue - where she lives now, and - that was a new house - then, yes. And - he died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You say he was out of work before you came along?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 That would have been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Or when I was very young, you know, one or two. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 That was before he went to the hat factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And what had he been doing before that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Be on the building. On the building. It was between that you see, and there wasn't any building being done evidently. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you know how long he was out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I don't know how long. I've heard my -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was there hardship in the family then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, it was then because there was no unemployment benefit and - I've heard
 my mother say she had to go blackberrying - to - and sell blackberries you know, to - get food with then. She pushed me in the pram so I can't remember you know but I've heard her tell about it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You'd have to go quite a long way to find blackberries too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well, no, I don't think you did those days. 'Cos Luton wasn't built up then. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 But it was still a little town I suppose, it had it's industries, it's hat factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. But it wasn't very - yes, but it wasn't very far out to the country, not really. No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You only went away on holiday actually if you went to a relation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 That's right, yes, St Albans was one of the places - I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Who lived at St Albans?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Moth - my mother's sister - an aunt of mine. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And would you go there for a week?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, week or fortnight sometimes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 All the family together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, no, not always, all depends - we did - we have done you know at times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 But sometimes you just went on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you tell me how you spent Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Saturday? Well in the morning it was cleaning and - in the afternoon then it would be shopping and - of course the shops used to keep open quite late, you know yes. Mm. Well I think - the market - I rememb
er Luton market being open air - and - I think - they used to keep open 'til nine o'clock. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And people used to go and shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 So you could have a really long shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You could. Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How would you spend your Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Had to go to Sunday school, morning and afternoon. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was it a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11951633\charrsid1799721 Methodist}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721  church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Yes. I remember my first Sunday school I went to North Street, and - it - it's still - it's a box factory now, and of course the other - the churc
h that was built opposite that's closed down and I think it's Seventh Day Adventists or something like that, and - I remember going there until we moved up to Round Green and then I went to Round Green Methodist, and I was there until a few years ago. Ten
 
years I should say, about ten years ago, when I actually left. I was in the Sunday school at seven years old, and then when I was fourteen I became a Sunday school teacher eventually and - I carried on, went, you know, right the way through. Yes, right 't
il I - until about ten years ago. Yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You went to actual Sunday school twice a day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. And - after Sunday school we had - in the morning you had to stay to the service 'til twelve o'clock - in the morning. And -

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What time would Sunday school start?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
At - ten, about ten I think, ten - ten to eleven then the service. You could go home you see, children did them days, used to go home but - did - I had to stay to the service, for the service, but was never expected to go at
 night, never had to go at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your parents go at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
No. No, they didn't go - regularly, my father was a Methodist. He belonged to the Central Mission, and of course that's - another one that's pulled down now. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did they go to the service that followed the Sunday school in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Why did you stay on, did you like to stay on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, they just told me I - I had to. It was their - it was their rule you know, and then go back -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And your brother as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Oh when he was old enough, yes. Yes. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have special clothes for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And they were clothes you only wore on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Wore for Sunday. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have to get changed when you came home from service?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Sometimes, not always. Not always. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were you allowed to play games on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well we didn't have to have toys out, not on Sunday, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What did you do with yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 We used to have to read or - look at books, we could look at books.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 But not have toys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, we didn't have toys out on Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your parents think it was wrong to work or play on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I think - it was the custom mostly those days you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They didn't have very strong views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
No. No. But I think it was just more - you know, custom not - mm, yes. Didn't have to go and play outside, not in the street or anything. No. Not then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 So it was a very quiet day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember being bored on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you remember any Sunday school outings, did they have any outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Sunday school - well the first ones I remember - at - from Round Green, it used to be in a field - called Ashc
roft, it's at Ashcroft Road and is - they call it - I don't know if you know Ashcroft - in Luton, it's on the outskirts of Luton, Stopsley Way, yes, we had to have it there because the war was on you know, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What would you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh - be races and - swings on trees. You know, big rope swings on the trees and - races mostly and play games you know in the field.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have a picnic?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh it was - they took - took tables and had the tea out on - it was out - on the tables outside li
ke and - set the tea, took all the - stuff over so you would call it a picnic, only it was tables and trestles. Yes. Oh yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How many children would there be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 I forget now. Quite a lot, yes. Mm. Yes, quite a lot. And then - after then I reme
mber going to one Sunday school outing to Ampthill in a brake. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What was at Ampthill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Just a field, you know, and it - the same sort of thing, make your own fun. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would that be once a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Once a year, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were there any other things the church used to organize?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, Christmas parties at Christmas, yes. For the children. It'd be after Christmas usually, just after Christmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did they have any young peoples clubs or adults clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Like a temperance group or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh well, there used to be - a Band of Hope we used to call it you know, for temperance meeting, Band of Hope, in the week time and -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your parents go to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, but - I think - we didn't have to go much no
t - in the evenings, not until we were older you know, they wouldn't let us out, not to go in the evenings, not to - different things. Not until we was getting about - twelve, you now, eleven or twelve then I could, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember whether a lot of people used to go to these Band of Hope meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes, I think there were, yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you say grace at home at mealtimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, but we always used to have to say thank you for - our meal afterwards you know, yes. Yes, we wasn't made to say grace you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have to kneel down beside the bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you and your brother say it together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, separately, but mother was in the room you know to hear us say it, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, no we didn't - do that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were you ever given lessons by your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Or a tutor or a governess?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How old were you when you started school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Where did you go to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 The first school I went to was Old Bedford Road. And - that was, you know, at the beginning and I - and then I went to Hitchin Road.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember your first day at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I don't think I know - I remember being at Old Bedford Road but I don't remember the first day actually. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What sort of school was it? Was it big?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh it's quite big, yes it's quite big.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And the classes are big are they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have one teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 One teach - yes, mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What time did you go in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Nine.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And when did you stop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well at the beginning you - I think it was about quarter past three isn't it, then it was quarter to four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you come home for lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you start when you started at five did you go all day or did you start with mornings only?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh no, all day, all day, yes. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was it a board school or a church school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, it's just the ordinary - a council school like, yes. Mm. Wasn't a church one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And it was a day school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Day school, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Walk. It wasn't very far to go - from North Street to the Bottom of North Street to Old Bedrord Road, wasn't t
oo far at all. 'Cos the school is still there only of course it's - had a bit put on it I think. Altered and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How long would it take you to walk to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh - not five minutes. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did mother come with you at first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh at first she did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Then you went by yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 After a bit, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have to take your brother when he started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, we did used to go together. Yes. Yes, we did go together, yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you mind taking him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you get a gang walking to school together, did you meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, sometimes, yes, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And you had your midday meal at home,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you like school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were you always happy there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. No, quite happy at school. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh - they seemed all right you know, yes, I thought so you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were you good at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You were quite clever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I was - I don't know about quite clever but I was - you know, quite good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You could keep up all right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were you better at any one thing than another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I don't think so. No, I don't think I was really. No, 'cos we only had the one teacher even in - at 
Hitchin Road when - in the school we only had standard one - to seven you know, I was in ex-seven two years. Mm. 'Til we left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What age did you leave?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Fourteen. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And right up to the end you only had one teacher per class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh - wel
l - year - in a year. I think - the - I only had two teachers the whole school through. In that - second school I went to, Hitchin Road, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What about the first school, did you always have the same teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I think I - we moved up, I had a
 teacher to move up with, and of course when I first went to Hitchin Road I went in to the infants but I wasn't - there very long, and then I had to go into the standard one, and - I had a teacher that took me up to about standard four, or standard five, 
and then I had a different teacher in standard six and seven. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And they would teach everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You wouldn't have a teacher for separate subjects?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, we did have - no, no, they teach you all, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you remember your t
eacher in the early days emphasising anything in particular, did she have any sort of bees in her bonnet about manners or punctuality or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I can't remember, not really, not in the early - no, no. Not in the early days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What about the way you spoke?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes - you had to talk properly you know. Yes. Mm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did she make you stand up and say good morning and things like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 If you did something wrong in school, or the other children, can you remember what would happen, what would be the punishment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well it used to be a cane. Across your hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you ever get it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Not very often, I did one - the odd time you know. Or - it'd either be a cane or a ruler, you know - across your hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What would you get the cane for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I don't really know. I've forgotten, you know,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Talking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes, you would, yes, for talking, if you talked when you - you shouldn't have.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did the girls get the same as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Well I don't really know. I couldn't say. It wasn't - it wasn't a - it wasn't a mixed school you know, they were separate, no. Yes, from the infants up, but in the infants -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 A separate playground?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Yes. Yes the girls school was one side and the boys the other. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you shout at each other across the playground?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, you couldn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was there a big wall between?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Well there - there's a road in between. A road across and - they have - one was the back you see and
 the other - back of the school, that was the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 So you were quite separate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your parents show an interest in your school work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes. Yes. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did they ever go and see the teacher or visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Ye
s. Yes. They did occasionally, you know, similar to they do now you know, go - have open day, it used to be called open day then, and then the parents used to go and see - your work. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were the other children from the same sort of home as yourself or were they mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I think they was a little bit mixed. Yes. Some were very poor you know and some were - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you remember the poor ones, were they badly dressed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Some of them were. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What did you other children think of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 We used to feel sorry for them, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you mix with them, play with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh sometimes, yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your parents tell you that you mustn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How about teachers, can you remember if they were harder on them than on you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I don't think they were, not really, no. No, I think -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were they naughtier, the poor ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 There were some, you know, there were some that were - a little bit - you know, out of hand how we'll put it you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would you say there were more of those or more of your sort?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, more - I - not so many - more of us sort I think, yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were there any gangs or groups in the school, did you have your own gangs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, we didn't used to not really, used to have friends you know but we didn't used to go about in gangs like, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were there any children who used to get left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 There may be you know, may be one or two that were probably, you know, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would they be poor children or shy children or what?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I think shy. Yes, I think shy. May be one or two poor ones you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You were fourteen when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would you have stayed longer if you could have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, you couldn't - not then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 But if it was possible would you have liked to have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
No, I don't think I would because I - I think I'd - you know - I'd been in ex-seven for two years and I - I - all I did the last twelve months was needlework. Yes. Mm. So I was really ready to leave, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you ever wish you'd had a better education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Oh sometimes, yes. Mm. Of course you could go in for - what we called modern school then, you know, from - but you had to win a scholarship for it, and - and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was that in the same town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was it in a separate place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Well the modern school was diff - there was a boys modern school and a boys - and a girls modern school, one was in Alexandra Avenue and the other was - Old Bedrod Road I think, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 That would be like a grammar school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, it is now. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You would have gone there when you were eleven or something like that would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, that's right. Mm hm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have the chance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No I didn't. I did - I missed it somehow, I don't know how it was but I did miss it you know and - I didn't -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were you sorry about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, I was, 'cos I would have liked to have gone. You know. But of course there was only - so many places too, so I mean you don't k
now whether - you would - there was some -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Still you were quite good at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
I was really, yes. Yes, I don't know how it was, you know that I missed it but - I don't - I might have been ill for a time you know, been away from school. I could have been, you know, when it -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11951633\charrsid1799721 Do you think you benefi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 ted from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes. Yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You still remember some of the things you learned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, quite a - mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How did you get on with your little brother, did you get on well with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes, yes, we got on very well really. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you play with him or with friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 We used to play with friends, but we used to play sometimes you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Five years is quite a big gap isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 It is really, yes. It is, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have special friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, I think - yes, and most of those were school friends you know, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Where did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well - we used to come - go and play into fields, in the summertime. Used to have - play into fields 
or - yes, they were fields at the top of the park, mostly fields but you could play on the roads those days you know, with a ball or skipping - used to play skipping and that outside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And did you play in your garden?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. We used to play in the garden too. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What other sort of games did you play, did you ever play rough games when you got dirty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, we did sometimes, I guess we did when we were out in the fields you know. Play rounders. Mm. Quite a lot. Yes.
