\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No, there
 wasn't any to belong to really. No, not even with the church there wasn't not then you know, only the - used to have Christian Endeavour but that was as I was getting older you see. We used to go to Christian Endeavour.
