\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, when you're fourteen and - that.
