\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You didn't bring them home and press them or anything?
