\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember some of the things you saw?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I remember one show at Drury Lane was called Good Luck. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How did you go there, in a train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 In the train, yes, and then undergr
ound. To a show. We used to have a day out in London when we used to go, used to have a day and then finish up with a theatre. Used to be a late night often, you know. And - it would be a special, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How about the cinema?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well it was just pict
ure show on Sat - well sometimes we used to go on Saturdays but I didn't used to go very much myself 'cos - I'm not - wasn't too fond of it not then. Not - going to the cinema.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was there a special children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10440261\charrsid1799721 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 s show in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have pocket money when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Very little - we used to have a - just a little but not much you know. Only coppers. Yes, it was just coppers then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And you had it every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What did you spend it on, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Sweets. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did anybody outside the house help your mother look after you or your brother at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, not really, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Any neighbours or friends who came in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh no. No, not to look after us, no. No, she didn't hav
e babysitters not then. Either went with them or not at all you know she didn't used to go outnights. They didn't -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Didn't they gout at night at all your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 If she were ill what would happen then, if your mother was ill and had to stay in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Me mother had to stay in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I think we - you know, make the best of it and - me father would - just, you know, help. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 He could do it if he had to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes. Yes, that's right, mm, he'd help make the best of it then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you have any aunts living nearby or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, not - not quite close no. In the town but not close.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They wouldn't come and help out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh no. No, they wouldn't - not to do anything, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember when your little brother was born, what happened then, did your mother have him at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
I think she must have had him at home but I don't remember a lot about it you know. No, I think she had him at home, they did them days I'm sure. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 An aunt didn't come then to look after you or help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
I - I would - think my grandmother did, my father's mother then 'cos she was alive then, you see. I think - and she lived in North Street and I would think she came down you know - really, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How much did your parents see of their relations living nearby in the town, did you visit one another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes - mostly - weekly or fortnightly, something like that you know, used to see them in turns. Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did they come to your house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your parents have many friends apart from relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, I think - they had neighbours you know, mostly neighbours, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And where would they have seen them? Would they have come to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes, yes, they used to visit you know to the house or - used to go to them. Sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your mother have special friends of her own and father his own friends or did they share them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, they used to be shared, you know, shared more or less, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Mother didn't have any friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I - no, I don't think she did, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 So they would have been mostly other married couples would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were friends into the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Parties, yes. Special occasions. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And they'd have eats and drinks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would you say the people invited in were your father's friends or mother's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh - well they shared friends. Both, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did friends come in casually without an invitation, were people dropping in much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Sometimes, just the occasion - occasionally. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And would neighbours drop in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Sometimes, yes, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did mother have them come in for a cup of tea or anything like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well - came - now and again but not very often, you know, not very often, just the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They didn't make a habit of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And your parents used to go and visit other friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did other friends have parties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes, oh yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would you be taken along?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And you said they used to make their own amusements?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Yes. That's right, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember people belonging to one class and some in another, people divided up into classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, you mean - like upper class, middle class and - poor class like really don't you, is that what you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. You can remember that can you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well yes I think it was more them days than it is now, yes. Yes, stayed - yes they did seem to you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you tell me what sort of class you think you belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I should say the middle class, what they'd call the middle class more or less, mm. I think majority of people did them days you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What other sort of people were in your class group? What sort of jobs did your parents friends have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Well mostly the everyday sort of jobs you know - I think - nothing - the - nothing, you know - really particular I don't think. I really can't say you know what sort. No, not what they - about the same, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They worked in the factories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, oh yes, in the factories more or less, with - with mother and father you know. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And when you say the poor class, what would they have been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well, they were very poor, there were a certain few t
hat were dressed very poor you know and looked very poor and - I don't know - whether it was through - it could have been through drink, this poor - this could have been caused - 'cos - the school I went to was down in - Charles Street, Hitchin Road and t
here was a lot - of class that lived around there where they used to - go drinking a lot and it was - the poor - the - poor, you know, poverty was caused through drink. Mostly, then. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 So they got the money but they spent it on drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Spend it on drink, I think that's what happened you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would they have been real labourers would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, I would say they were labourers, yes, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What about classes above you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well - no, I don't think I would really you know, I didn't sort of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What would you have thought of has being the upper class, what sort of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well - little bit difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Doctors would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well - could be but - just those you know -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How about the people who were the heads of the factories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 That lived - yes, mm, and those that lived on big estates you know, those sort of people I would say - really. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 There was a brewery wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes - Park Street, but I didn't know much about it you know, I'm just not - and things like that. YES? THAT would be those.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How about the vicar and people like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Well, yes, they were in those days more - on the upper crust, they didn't mix with you like they do now. I - I've found that out, yes, mm. Oh I think the ministers are much more sociable with you now - you know, these days than they used to be, oh yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They used to just stick to upper class people did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, more or less, yes, I think they did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you remember being told to treat certain people with respect, perhaps to say sir or madam or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Not to curtsey or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 NO. You always addressed a doctor as Doctor you know, but - but not sir, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember anybody showing respect to your parents in these ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I don't think I do, no. Not calling them sir, no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Who were considered the most important people in your life do you think? In the area, who were the important people of the town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Well I'd say the councillors, you know, councillors and - Town Crier and those sort of people - really, yes, and Justice of the Peace, you know, those sort of - you know -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What would they have been, a Justice of the Peace, would they have been doctors or factory owners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. Some of them would be in business I should say, you know, factory owners and - things like that, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Why were they considered important, did you come into contact with them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They were generally thought to be important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Thought to be, yes, I think so, yes. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What about shopkeepers, who would they have associated with, what sort of class were they thought to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well, I can't - not quite sure about that really, I can't - say - but I should say the middle class. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What about your local shop, how did you think about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Well I think you'd think about them as - as middle class more or less but I think some of them did think they were the upper class you know, yes. Yes, that's right, yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And the vicars you think associated with the upper class more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh - well I think they did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How about teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well - no, I - of course apart from being at school we didn't have - anything to do wit
h them like apart from being - no, no, apart from being at school you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And the employers, did you see anything of them, would your father have seen anything of his employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. I think he was very nice - my father's employer, Mr Barfo
rd, although - they were redundant you know when the work - but still - yes, I think; Mr Barford was very nice with the workers. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did he live locally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, Bedford. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was he very rich, did you think he was rich?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I should imagine so really, yes, I would think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you ever see him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm hm. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did he come to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No, but I've been to the factory and I've seen him at the factory. Well we was allowed to go down to the factory. Yes. Mm. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would you spend the day there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh no. No - well - when - when my father probably was - doing a late shift or - anything like that and he's been there and I've seen him.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Would he speak to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What did he look like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Oh - I know he had a beard - this - Mr Barford did you know, he was very nice. Yes, and he - you know, he'd speak to you and - was very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did he look after his workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes, I think he did, yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Who would his friends be, other employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 I should say other employers. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Other people in business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm, I would think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What was the difference between the people who went to church and the people who went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 I don't thin
k there's any difference really, shouldn't be. No, but - I think those that went to church felt - a little bit more - you know, than - they were a little bit higher than those went to chapel, they - we'll put it that way. Mm. I think they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 It's funny that isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Mm, it is.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Where you lived did all the people in the working class or your sort of people, you say you were middle class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 I don't mean the really poor.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, no, the working class then, perhaps - perh
aps you'd term it as working class. Only I thought there was just the three you know, the middle - yes, some - yes, but I think them days they did call it more middle class than - than working class. Yes. No, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 But in your class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did they all have roughly the same standard of living or were they different, did your friends homes seem the same to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, about the same I should say, mm. Yes, more or less, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you remember going to the home of a really poor person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Not when I was young, no. No. Not when I was young. I have - you know, since I've been older - like, but not while I was young, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How old would you have been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well the first time was when I done visiting from the chu - the church, and I should say in my late teens more you know, eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember being taken to a sort of posh house when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Not when I was little, no, but I've been in some since you know. Yes. Not when I was little, no. Not really, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you ever get to know a family in the very poor class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I don't think I would, not - not to - put any -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You can't remember any particular times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, no, I wouldn't say as I would, not to - put them out you know, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were there some families who were thought of as very rough and others as respectable, can you remember hearing about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 About rough people, yes, I did, you know, and - when they used to fight. Is that the sort of roughness you mean? Yes. There were s
ome in Hitchin Road, I've heard about them, I've not seen but I heard about them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 But they would be mostly among the poor people?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was there any sort of fighting or drinking among the sort of people your parents knew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They were all respectable were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Do you remember a difference between men who had a craft, craftsmen who'd served apprenticeships and ordinary labourers who could just turn their hand to anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember a difference between them, did one feel themselves difference from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Mm, but I don't know. 'Cos I didn't really know a - you know, real craftsmen not a lot you see and you know. And -we should think most of them -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember them feeling that they were any better?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I don't know that - they did really. No, I don't think so, no, I can't really say much about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes? Did mother 
feel that she was a better class than your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh no, no, I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They felt the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes, I think they were too you know more or less. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And did they feel the same towards other classes, one of them wouldn't forbid you to go and play with poor children and the other not?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No. Oh no, no,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They usually agreed about things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you ever remember a family or anybody moving from one class to another? Was it possible to make good?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well I guess it was but I don't know of anybody but I should think it would be really you know. Unless they -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did anybody sink from the respectable down to be very poor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, not as I know, you know, I don't know of, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you remember people being described as real gentlemen or real ladies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well yes I have heard them say, yes, I have heard them say that you know but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What do you think they meant by that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well - I don't quite know. I should think w
hen they - you know, really be - doing any - good - you know, and that - when they've being doing good and they say well she's real - lady and real gentleman, and it - it -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 It was more to do with what they were doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Doing - yes, I think so. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Not how much money they had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
No, no. No, with - what they were doing - actually and especially if they had money and they were doing good you know - sort of thing. Mm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember seeing a policeman around when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. They used to be walking around on beat. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were you frightened of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 A bit. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your mother ever say, if you're naughty I'll call a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Mm. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How do you think the police treated people? Were they nicer or worse than they are now do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well, I don't know really. I suppose they were - they were nice really you know. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Were the people sort of frightened of them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I think you were frightened of policemen thos
e days more than you are now. Yes. Mm. I don't think you was actually frightened of the man, it was of their position. You know. Really. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 They were held perhaps more in respect then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, they were, yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Your house was rented, did you ever see anything of the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh yes, he used to call every week. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 For his rent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Mm. Yes. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your parents like him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Got on all right, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Can you remember times when your parents had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Parents - I think, you know, I think they had to sort of work out every week you know, but - I didn't know - you know, any particular struggle like, only of course I didn't remember not when I was very young you see, no. No. A
nd of course when - my dad was out of work in 1929 I mean it wasn't for many weeks and he found this other job, and then of course then he was taken ill and he didn't get over his illness, see, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember him being ill when you were very little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
No. No. No. I know he didn't go into the - he couldn't go into the 1914/18 war because he had a weak heart, I do know that, and that's why he kept on down at the factory you know, bleach and dye works, I do know that, he wasn't able to go into 
the war. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did he mind about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
No. No, he didn't mind. No, 'cos he had to wear - remember him having to wear an arm band, you know. Yes, to say that he was rejected you see, yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did you ever have any help from any sort of charity do you remember?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 The Parish or the Guardians?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No. No, nothing like that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember if there was somebody in the area who people disapproved of if they were very rough and made a noise or were a nuisance, c
an you remember what the rest of the neighbourhood would do about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You don't remember anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, I don't - no, I don't remember any - I mean - no, because I don't - you know, there wasn't anything like that where I live
d and I - not in Morton Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 You were all much the same sort of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you know what his views were? What he voted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well - 
I think he voted for the man more than the - you know, for the - party, but I do know he - he voted Conservative - once or twice, yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And what about mother, what did mother vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 I don't know. No, I think more or less the same you know but I don't really -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 She followed father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Yes, I think she did. I don't know - was - was she allowed to vote in them days? I'm not quite sure about it, it was only the father at first but - when she did - when she was allowed to vote I think she sort of followed him. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember them voting in a general election before 1919?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Yes - I'd be twelve. No, I don't really know. No. I can't remember dad - I - I remember when he did - who he voted for when he voted Conservative you know, I remember that man's name but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Who was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 O'Connor. Mm. Yes. And - and - oh, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And your father thought he was a good man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes, and another time - I think he - he voted Liberal he was Liberal before then. 'Cos mostly the people w
ere Liberal you know, used to be Liberal and Conservative mostly. That's before the Labour came in to being - really, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And Luton was Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 It was really, yes. Was really. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you ever remember him having to vote the same as his employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh no. No. They - oh were they, no, no, he was free to vote who he - wants, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was he a member of any political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 He never worked for a party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Or mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did they ever take part in politics except at voting time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How did they spend their spare time, your parents, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Just about the house were they?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Mostly, yes. And then the gardening, used to go out to the allotment in the summertime you know, in the evenings and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No, she didn't, no, she didn't do anything particularly like, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did she ever go out on her own to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh no, no, if 
they went they went together when we were old enough, you know - to be left or take with - taken with - takes us with them, and that was just pictures you know, used to go to the pictures one - once a week. Oh my mother did - oh - but that was in later - 
when we were getting older she used to go to a football match with my father, on a Saturday afternoon. Yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Luton Town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. It wasn't - was Luton Town, yes. Yes. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What time did your father get home from work in the evening, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Well - used to be seven o'clock. Yes, it - oh yes, he used to work - work quite late. And - mostly - mostly it was seven you know, yes. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What would he do in the evening, just sit and have a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. But - I don't kno
w whether he used to have - used to have midday cooked meal you know, then he used to - think he used to come home to tea, and then go back again. That's - yes, what they did. The only meal he took was his breakfast in the morning because he used to go - 
quite early you know and - used to take - well he used to make a cup of tea or mother used to do it and - used to go and - take his breakfast and he'd have a break then for breakfast you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What would he take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Sandwiches. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How many evenings a week would be spent at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh every evening, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 With the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. Yes.
\par 
