\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 A pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Not to the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Was he a drinking man at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No not at all. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And mother not either?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No. Not to - no, not to the pubs, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 And your mother didn't go to a club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No, she didn't belong to anything. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did father take part in any sport, he washed the football?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 He used to foll - that's all. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Did he play anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How about races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No, No, he didn't used to - interest in racing or like that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 He didn't have a bet on anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Do you remember if they belonged to any savings clubs, like they used to save up towards being sick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Oh - oh yes. Yes, my dad did, he belonged to the Central Mission, and - another one at St Paul's church I think he used to. You know, and then when they were off sick they used to have so much - didn't they - given them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Run by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 
Yes. Yes. The Central Mission still does run only its a High Town church now. Yes. 'Cos I'm in the lady's one, yes, still. I had thought of giving it up 'cos I only pay once a quarter when I have to go to a friend, and - mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 What about things like funeral money, people used to pay in towards funerals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Yes. But I don't know - my mother hasn't done anything like that, no. But they used to pay in for doctor. 'Cos when - yes, used t
o pay him so much a week you know for a doctor, when we were small. So - you know, for us children. Yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How about clothes or shoes or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Oh no, didn't used to pay anything like that, not for them, she used to save it herself until there was enough to buy what we needed. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16210540 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 How about things for Christmas, like Christmas clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5194681 HM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12976432\charrsid1799721 Well there were Christmas clubs but I don't know whether my mum and dad belonged to them, I don't think they did. No. No.
\par }}